### Centrality Algorithms

**1. Degree Centrality:**
```python
def degree_centrality(G):
    centrality = {}
    n = G.number_of_nodes()

    for node in G.nodes():
        # Weighted degree
        degree = sum(G[node][neighbor]['weight'] 
                    for neighbor in G.neighbors(node))
        centrality[node] = degree / (n - 1) if n > 1 else 0

    return centrality

# Or use NetworkX
degree_cent = nx.degree_centrality(G)
